<title>SOUTH AFRICA: CTP, Hortors study new plans.</title>
<headline>CTP, Hortors study new plans.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1996-08-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>CTP Holdings Ltd said it was considering various measures to implement an offer to Hortors Ltd minority shareholders after an earlier scheme of arrangement failed to win court approval.</p>
<p>Shareholders were advised to exercise caution in their dealings.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
